Class PromelaInPredicateVisitor

java.lang.Object
  h2PFoundation.NodeUtilityClass
      h2PVisitors.aVisitor
          h2PVisitors.PromelaInPredicateVisitor

public class PromelaInPredicateVisitor
extends aVisitor

Uses the Expression Grammar to find "in" predicates in an expression in order to build an INPredicateTarget list for a given model.
